WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:08:04.599
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:11.554
I'm so thankful that there are so many of you who want to pray with us this late at night.

00:08:11.555 --> 00:08:17.759
Welcome and good evening, family. Good early morning to all of you.

00:08:17.760 --> 00:08:22.955
I'm going to go over some of the things the Lord showed us in this last video.

00:08:22.956 --> 00:08:37.079
I was praying over some of the correction the Lord gave me; He corrected me on how I communicate because I don't want to bring fear to you.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:58.402
He said, 'Brandon, don't bring fear to their hearts. Warn them and walk away from it.'You don't have to scare the elderly or the young; just present what I show you and walk away.

00:08:58.403 --> 00:09:08.761
How they handle it is between Me and them. It is about how you communicate, and I'm learning.

00:09:08.762 --> 00:09:19.488
When it comes to the plague and the things the Lord has shown me, I truly believe with all my heart that when you are in the cleft of the rock, no weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:09:19.489 --> 00:09:26.121
I always want to drive that home: God always provides a way of escape for the believer.

00:09:26.122 --> 00:09:32.733
He showed Joseph the seven years of plenty and the seven years of famine.

00:09:32.734 --> 00:09:40.013
He showed Noah to build the ark. He's always had a way. He's the waymaker.

00:09:40.014 --> 00:09:47.479
He will always provide the way. He doesn't leave His kids high and dry and say, 'Well, you know what?

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:57.579
You're on your own, pal.'He's always there saying, 'I love you and I've got a plan for your life.'That's why I try to tell you, you can't derail your life if you're seeking Jesus.

00:09:57.580 --> 00:10:15.503
If your heart is seeking Him, the Bible says, 'Those that seek Me will find Me.'What the devil meant for bad, God will turn around for good in your life. If you're actively pursuing Him, you will find Him.

00:10:15.504 --> 00:10:28.902
If you're being lazy and sitting on your 'blessed assurance'and not pursuing the Lord or having a relationship with Him, His hands are tied on some things, but He'll keep that nudging at your heart.

00:10:28.903 --> 00:10:37.365
My dad was telling me tonight about growing potatoes in sacks and having creative ideas for it.

00:10:37.366 --> 00:10:46.328
He said he put dirt in the sack, and one sack produces 100 pounds in a gunny sack.

00:10:46.329 --> 00:10:59.231
He said, 'Son, I'm going to be able to produce 100 pounds per sack of potatoes, and with three sacks, that'll be 300 pounds of potatoes when it's all said and done.'Dad's always thinking and prepping.

00:10:59.232 --> 00:11:06.358
It's interesting because everybody is listening to the Lord for themselves and what He's telling them to do.

00:11:06.359 --> 00:11:10.322
Is there fear in that? No. My dad's not afraid; people aren't afraid.

00:11:10.323 --> 00:11:16.719
When you're listening to the voice of the Lord, He will lead and guide you on what you're supposed to be doing.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:35.249
Whenever He spoke to the people about turning water into wine, Mary said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.'They followed His instruction.

00:11:35.250 --> 00:11:40.833
He could instruct you to do something totally different than what He's telling my dad.

00:11:40.834 --> 00:11:46.569
The Lord didn't tell me to use a gunny sack full of potatoes, but He's talking to my dad about it.

00:11:46.570 --> 00:11:53.889
I thought that was interesting. You have to follow the voice of God for what He's telling you to do.

00:11:53.890 --> 00:12:24.205
When I'm bringing up things about the end times, whether you live in New York, Oklahoma, or California, your instruction is going to be different than mine because you live in a different area or climate. You just have to follow the voice.

00:12:24.206 --> 00:12:47.800
As the major scripture for last night says, 'For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.'I believe with all my heart that you don't need a prophetic voice holding your hand.

00:12:47.801 --> 00:13:02.262
His sheep will hear His voice, and a stranger's voice they will not follow. You have to be His and abide in Him.

00:13:02.263 --> 00:13:21.004
'If ye abide in Me and My words remain in you, you will ask what you will and it shall be done.'There are qualifications for a relationship with God: abiding in His Word and having fellowship with Him daily.

00:13:21.005 --> 00:13:32.399
It takes practice and time. Practice His presence. Spend time with the Father every day in prayer and reading His Word.

00:13:32.400 --> 00:13:40.599
Get into the scripture and make it real to you. When it becomes rhema to you, that's whenever it will work for you.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:49.839
Until then, you're just parroting. You have a relationship because of intimacy with Him, not just because your pastor tells you to.

00:13:49.840 --> 00:14:11.599
Everything is about intimacy with Him. If your pastor or spiritual leader dies tomorrow, do you have an intimate relationship or will it completely derail you?

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:22.519
You must find Jesus for yourself. Your pastor can't get you there; your relative can't get you there.

00:14:22.520 --> 00:14:47.479
You are the only one who will stand before the Father alone. I will stand before my Creator alone, and you must find Him alone.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:15:03.542
There's so much truth to the song 'I Come to the Garden Alone.'When I tell you what the Lord is saying, it's not to scare you.

00:15:03.543 --> 00:15:10.399
We love you, but if you're scared, I believe it's because He's trying to shake you to wake you up.

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:25.074
On January 1, the Lord said 2026 will be the year of 1 Corinthians 5:5. I am going to shake the church and its leadership.

00:15:25.075 --> 00:15:37.723
There will be people here at the beginning of the year who won't be here very long; they're about to go home.

00:15:37.724 --> 00:15:46.079
You will see great leaders in great positions not be here anymore, and their ministries will soon close down.

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:59.040
The Lord said judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:15:59.041 --> 00:16:05.386
He said there's corruption in big ministries that I'm going to deal with this year.

00:16:05.387 --> 00:16:13.159
Some will be standing behind pulpits and fall over dead right there, like Ananias and Sapphira.

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:28.079
I saw people preaching, and they went home right there. The Lord said there will be mega-ministries that will no longer be here this year.

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:36.759
There will be transitions in ministries, and they'll say, 'What about my legacy?

00:16:36.760 --> 00:17:10.664
Who's going to take over after I'm gone?'I see these generals going home and new Davids rising up.

00:17:10.665 --> 00:17:29.300
I see a passing of the baton coming on an even greater scale. I waited as they asked me to stay longer.

00:17:29.301 --> 00:17:37.108
But the door is coming and a passing of the baton. I see a certain general asking to stay longer.

00:17:37.109 --> 00:17:38.696
Could he stay longer? Because he told them they're coming home.

00:17:38.697 --> 00:17:43.999
And he said, "No, this time you'll see a passing of the baton.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:50.279
A door will open, they will walk through, and there will be a passing of the baton.

00:17:50.280 --> 00:18:01.586
It was about their legacy. The Lord said it was about legacy. They asked him, 'What will happen to my legacy?

00:18:01.587 --> 00:18:12.439
I must pray and cultivate to make sure of my legacy.'And now you'll see. They've been on borrowed time.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:18.918
This is what they said because a new generation is coming and I see a passing of the baton.

00:18:18.919 --> 00:18:41.340
They would say, 'What about the legacy of what I leave with this ministry?'I hear this in the spirit realm. They'll start to go home.

00:18:41.341 --> 00:18:52.753
The Lord wouldn't let me talk about it because I saw the individual who it was and the Lord said, 'Don't you dare touch that.'And so the Lord told me to bring that up again.

00:18:52.754 --> 00:19:06.479
There will be a lot of transition coming in the days ahead. Mega ministers will soon go home.

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:11.346
And the Lord said, 'Brandon, this is what a transition will be for 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:19:11.347 --> 00:19:27.159
You will see a shaking that will awaken to bring the bride by my side.'I touched that lightly, but I want you to see this right here.

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:52.319
This was January 23rd, 2026. I told you 1 Corinthians 5:5 was the word of the Lord for 2026.

00:19:52.320 --> 00:19:59.456
A lot of people didn't want to hear that. But I said you're going to see great leaders in California fall.

00:19:59.457 --> 00:20:06.959
There will be great church shaking in California in the days ahead.

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:20.420
A major leader of a major church in California will be shaken and things will be exposed.

00:20:20.421 --> 00:20:31.399
I said it will go all over the media, but I've not touched it. The Lord said, 'I'm shaking churches, Brandon.

00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:39.513
I'm exposing corruption.'He said, 'A major TV network won't be there very much longer.

00:20:39.514 --> 00:20:53.719
They'll go down, too.'I've warned about this many times. There's corruption in TV networks, churches, and major ministries.

00:20:53.720 --> 00:21:03.720
And he said, 'Brandon, I'm cleaning house.'There will be great shaking in the church in the days ahead.

00:21:03.721 --> 00:21:11.099
Ministers that used to have huge platforms and audiences will no longer be there, just that fast.

00:21:11.100 --> 00:21:25.359
You'll see new faces rise up out of seemingly nowhere that I will put my hand on, and I will use them and bring my glory through them—not for us to hold it, but to deflect.

00:21:25.360 --> 00:21:43.599
We're just vessels: the janitors, the cooks, the children's church workers, the parking lot attendants, people who have been broken and been on the potter's wheel for such a time as this.

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:54.510
He will use whoever says, 'Yes, here am I, Lord,'without an ego or a resume. He's done with egos and resumes.

00:21:54.511 --> 00:22:03.218
He's looking for the person who says, 'I cleaned vomit and poo for years and just wanted to yield to the Father.

00:22:03.219 --> 00:22:17.119
I was the guy pulling weeds or cleaning up dirty diapers in the parking lot to the glory of God.'That's what he is looking for right now.

00:22:17.120 --> 00:22:33.599
Not someone who says, 'I have a doctorate in theology and can out-school everyone; I have world knowledge of the Bible,'but has no character.

00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:58.999
He's looking for people with character who will not bend. You're going to see an exposing in this.

00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:09.759
This is 1 Corinthians 5:5 coming to full fruit. We're seeing things in the church.

00:23:09.760 --> 00:23:38.548
The Lord said, 'You'll see big churches, TV stations, and mega ministers on the platform who will be no more.'They'll have to resign because of buried sin.

00:23:38.549 --> 00:24:07.129
The Lord said, 'I am cleansing my house. 2026 will be a year of cleansing.'Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:24:07.130 --> 00:24:18.624
Because of this, I will also clean the world and you'll start to see the manifestations of it in 2026—politicians and more.

00:24:18.625 --> 00:24:39.736
This has been on my heart today. The Lord was talking to me about martyrs and said there will be many in the days ahead.

00:24:39.737 --> 00:24:49.825
I was bothered by this. I saw individuals I knew who are no longer here.

00:24:49.826 --> 00:25:13.719
The Lord warned me, 'Brandon, every one of my disciples except one was martyred.'He was warning about the shaking that was coming.

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:17.224
There are things the church doesn't want to touch because they're uncomfortable.

00:25:17.225 --> 00:25:35.303
They don't want to hear when the Lord says, 'I'm out of time,'or address a church that is complacent and lukewarm.

00:25:35.304 --> 00:25:44.787
The Lord said he'd rather you be hot or cold; if you're lukewarm, he'll spew you out of his mouth.

00:25:44.788 --> 00:26:04.438
The modern church on social media doesn't want to hear that—skinny jeans, fog machines, and 30-minute sermonette with offerings to build their own kingdoms.

00:26:04.439 --> 00:26:16.796
The Lord said, 'I'm done with the way they handle money. I'm going to judge how they have manipulated things.'The Lord said, 'Never ask my people for anything publicly.

00:26:16.797 --> 00:26:19.802
Never solicit my people. If they want to give, that's between me and them.'Diana and I have set out to do that.

00:26:19.803 --> 00:26:26.002
People say, 'Brandon, I want to bless your family or help buy Bibles.'That's because God put it on their hearts.

00:26:26.003 --> 00:26:26.102
I put links in the description for those who feel led because they asked.

00:26:26.103 --> 00:27:00.806
But I've never come on here and pleaded for help to build a TV station.

00:27:00.807 --> 00:27:14.252
The Lord has put big things in my heart, but I've never asked. He has given us huge things to do.

00:27:14.253 --> 00:27:40.279
The Lord said, 'I'm done with the way church has been; it's a stench to the world's nose.'He wants people to receive the word without a bad taste in their mouths.

00:27:40.280 --> 00:27:47.559
People are upset about the prosperity message, though I believe with all my heart that God wants us blessed.

00:27:47.560 --> 00:27:52.155
Give, and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together.

00:27:52.156 --> 00:27:59.234
People get mad about it and throw rocks, and the world won't even have anything to do with the church.

00:27:59.235 --> 00:28:02.892
Then we have the great falling away that I believe with all my heart.

00:28:02.893 --> 00:28:18.319
When we've prophesied and said all the things the Lord has told us to say on this channel, it was to warn you about what everybody else is talking about right now: Amanda and Joseph and all.

00:28:18.320 --> 00:28:30.243
We've been saying it for three or four years now, and I'm thankful someone else is saying it other than us. You all need to know what's coming.

00:28:30.244 --> 00:28:45.399
Thank God for Paul Begley and some of these others who are coming up saying, 'Listen: alarm, alarm, alarm.'The senators are saying it, but we don't need the senators to say it; the Lord already told us it was coming before the senators wanted to have a meeting.

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:52.519
You heard it from the Holy Spirit first. It's not being flaky; it's being in the news now.

00:28:52.520 --> 00:28:58.702
We're not trying to pat ourselves on the back. The Lord told us to warn you as a watchman on the wall.

00:28:58.703 --> 00:29:06.649
There's a great shaking coming with a plague and financial shaking more than what you've ever known.

00:29:06.650 --> 00:29:17.319
I've said that for years because you are hard-headed, and He has to tell you repeatedly because you don't have ears to hear.

00:29:17.320 --> 00:29:20.652
It's like I was telling a pastor today on the phone as we talked.

00:29:20.653 --> 00:29:36.644
The Lord said, 'Remember when I told you the angel came to me?'An angel came with the most beautiful sapphire blue eyes—pools of blue eyes—and he said, 'Hush now.'He put his hand on my lips.

00:29:36.645 --> 00:29:42.113
This was a real man of a savior. He went, 'Hush now. They're not dead to self. They can't hear.

00:29:42.114 --> 00:29:54.809
He that has ears to hear, let him hear what the Spirit is saying.'And they don't have ears to hear; therefore, even if they heard it from you, they're not hearing it from the Holy Spirit.

00:29:54.810 --> 00:30:00.439
Because they're not hearing it from the Lord, they'll lose it all or it will destroy them.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:08.599
You're not accountable to make them hear it; you're accountable just to repeat what the Holy Spirit has told you to say.

00:30:08.600 --> 00:30:14.496
Remember, 'Be still, son.'That's what the Lord kept saying to me.

00:30:14.497 --> 00:30:22.758
And then the angel would say, 'Hush now.'Now, the Lord kept telling me in my heart—the angel didn't call me son.

00:30:22.759 --> 00:30:30.875
I need to make that clear because I have 'Sister Clipboard'going, 'That angel called you son?'No, the Lord said, 'Be still, son.

00:30:30.876 --> 00:30:54.479
Hush now, son.'And the angel would say, 'Hush. Be still.'I have to make that clear because I know you have the trolls.

00:30:54.480 --> 00:31:08.798
In all that I say, the Lord shows me, in my opinion, concerning when I said, 'Watch the holly berry bush.'The berries will turn red and everybody that was standing on a rug—the stock market.

00:31:08.799 --> 00:31:28.714
I said the snow will fall when there were no leaves on the trees, and the angel said, 'Watch the winter months.'You ask, 'When?'I will not tell you the year because I am not a financial advisor, but I saw it happen in the winter months.

00:31:28.715 --> 00:31:34.543
The angel came to me and said, 'In the winter months.'Brandon, please tell me.

00:31:34.544 --> 00:31:50.870
No, find Him yourself. It's not my job to spoon-feed you. I point you in the direction to pray and find Him for yourself.

00:31:50.871 --> 00:31:57.725
Then I let go of the rope and say, 'Listen, it's not my job anymore.'But I say: pray.

00:31:57.726 --> 00:32:12.879
The angel said, 'Watch the holly berry bush.'What year, Brandon? What month? It's not my problem. Is that rude?

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:23.850
No, it's love because you always have people that will ride the wind of someone else's revelation and could miss it.

00:32:23.851 --> 00:32:44.865
You could be off. That is dangerous. You must find Him for yourself. Play the next clip and then let's pray tonight.

00:32:44.866 --> 00:33:02.745
This is when I first heard it—it was during the Christmas from the White House. There's a shaking in the churches.

00:33:02.746 --> 00:33:21.279
You will see a great breaking in the churches and they will come to their knees, for there is heresy and a shaking.

00:33:21.280 --> 00:33:33.656
It's a stench before Him each day. True repentance is to turn away.

00:33:33.657 --> 00:33:43.211
You're going to see that even in the highest places in the land and on TV. If you're a friend of the world, you're not a friend of Me.

00:33:43.212 --> 00:33:49.070
He said, 'Tell them: if you're a friend of the world, you're not a friend of Me.

00:33:49.071 --> 00:34:00.280
You've cleaved to the world and you've not clung to Me.'Depart from Me, I never knew you.

00:34:00.281 --> 00:34:21.099
For there are many walking in heresy. Just because you tried to walk with the president or these people, you see this heresy.

00:34:21.100 --> 00:34:29.426
It's messy. He says it's messy unto Him. It's gross, it's stinky. Too much pride.

00:34:29.427 --> 00:34:54.474
'I resist the proud.'He said, 'Humble yourself unto Me.'In due time, I would exalt you, but there has not been time for many of them.

00:34:54.475 --> 00:35:04.746
They've exalted themselves. He is angry about this. I hear His voice.

00:35:04.747 --> 00:35:20.568
The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom. Reverence, holiness, and purity back in My church.

00:35:20.569 --> 00:35:32.223
You don't even know the difference between the church and the world today, He said. Yet you say you're of Me and you're My church.

00:35:32.224 --> 00:35:40.959
This is in the purest of circles that you think you see, for there's great heresy and shaking on them.

00:35:40.960 --> 00:35:59.279
Even in the ones that try to pretend that they're the purest, their hearts are far from Me.

00:35:59.280 --> 00:36:11.559
You don't have to yank on a horse's mouth hard to pull it off when it's in order.

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:23.959
You don't have to yank on the bridle of a horse's mouth to make it have great correction if the horse is in line with you.

00:36:23.960 --> 00:36:38.318
It just takes a little bit to guide it. But when a horse is rebellious and bucking around, it takes much strength.

00:36:38.319 --> 00:36:41.352
When you're on track with Me, it doesn't take much correction.

00:36:41.353 --> 00:36:58.559
You barely have to pull it. It doesn't take much to guide a broken horse.

00:36:58.560 --> 00:37:44.100
But when you are not broken or pliable, it takes much to break. Oh, He longs for you to have a relationship with Him.

00:37:44.101 --> 00:38:00.879
He says, 'You've grieved the heart of the Father.'He's provided so much for you, but you've grieved His heart.

00:38:00.880 --> 00:38:05.803
Oh, Father, we repent. Oh, forgive them. Father, forgive me, Lord.

00:38:05.804 --> 00:38:15.799
We come closer to you. You're such a good God. We repent, Lord.

00:38:15.800 --> 00:38:27.433
He said, "You say you want the revival, you say you want the glory, but you have so much of the world in you.

00:38:27.434 --> 00:38:34.080
Separate yourself unto me, and you will see the great glory."There's a remnant of you that have done just this.

00:38:34.081 --> 00:38:42.719
You've separated yourself unto me, and you're ready for the glory, but you are few.

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:55.199
He said it reminds him of what it was when Moses came down off the mountain and the children of Israel were acting the way they did.

00:38:55.200 --> 00:39:09.015
They built a calf and did things in rebellion unto me. But I will use the remnant, and there are great days to come.

00:39:09.016 --> 00:39:19.599
He's sending his angel armies, and there'll be a great revival in the churches that will allow him to flow, but also a great shaking.

00:39:19.600 --> 00:39:27.599
He's talking about Asia; I see South Korea again. Great persecution.

00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:41.559
He's ready to turn the page, a new chapter. He's out of time. That's why we try to warn you tonight.

00:39:41.560 --> 00:39:45.358
The Lord's out of time. He's not out of mercy, but he's out of time.

00:39:45.359 --> 00:39:53.908
Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and gentlemen, and he's coming sooner than you think. There are many of you that are not ready.

00:39:53.909 --> 00:40:04.959
If Jesus Christ was coming back this week or this year, are you ready for the coming of the Lord?

00:40:04.960 --> 00:40:12.995
You must search your heart and know him. You must find him for yourself, for a shaking to awaken is coming.

00:40:12.996 --> 00:40:25.759
With all this being said by aliens and all the things going on right now, people are freaking out and it's even hitting the world news.

00:40:25.760 --> 00:40:32.725
What is the pastor saying? A great falling away is about to take place.

00:40:32.726 --> 00:40:42.279
I want to tell you that there are many of you who feel you're right and you're not; it's time to come home tonight.

00:40:42.280 --> 00:40:52.039
Or you may be here saying, "Brandon, I feel that shaking inside of me and I feel the fear of God tonight. I want to know him.

00:40:52.040 --> 00:41:04.879
I want to repent, turn from my wicked ways, and come home."I want to run to Jesus tonight and be on the right side of this.

00:41:04.880 --> 00:41:18.994
I want to be used for the end-time glory—to be that vessel that is on fire, saying, "God, here am I. Use me. Put the coal on my lips.

00:41:18.995 --> 00:41:32.113
Do whatever you've got to do."I want to be at the spout where the glory comes out and feel the presence of God on my life and take it to the nations.

00:41:32.114 --> 00:41:44.948
There was a man—this is a true story—who was in a revival with a minister.

00:41:44.949 --> 00:41:56.212
He went to the barber to get his haircut. Another man walks in and says, "There's something wrong with you.

00:41:56.213 --> 00:42:06.519
What's going on?"He thought he had crumbs on his face, but the man said, "No, you have sparkles on your face. You're glowing.

00:42:06.520 --> 00:42:26.145
What is going on with the sparkles on your face?"Well, he had just come from the meeting that morning where the glory of the Lord was imparted with the laying on of hands.

00:42:26.146 --> 00:42:45.598
He didn't realize that he took it with him, and when the sinner came in off the street, he saw the glory sparkling on him.

00:42:45.599 --> 00:42:55.039
The man was born again and baptized in the Holy Ghost right there in the barbershop.

00:42:55.040 --> 00:43:05.178
What a way to be a witness in these last days! You don't have to pass out tracts. You can be passing out the glory on your face.

00:43:05.179 --> 00:43:18.550
When people see that you arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord has risen on you, they're going to say there's something different about you.

00:43:18.551 --> 00:43:45.599
